Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:08.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一周前  从第一次出现受害者时起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:18.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续虚空爆炸事件的爆炸威力以及范围正在不断扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:18.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:27.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有发现时间和地点的关联性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:32.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对遗留物品进行的取样分析中也没有找到线索
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止出现下一个受害者  必须与警备员相互协助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:38.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进一步强化各种的警备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并全力以赴解决此次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:28.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚也一直调查到深夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚空爆炸事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:29.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:37.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搜索没有进展的情况下  就不得不确认一下有没有漏掉线索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热衷于工作虽然是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那么担心黑子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:51.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么如果今晚能同床共枕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子  小小的疲劳马上就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  姐姐大人真是个容易害羞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AIM扩散力场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对能力者来说是非常贴近身边的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓AIM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:22.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是An Involuntary Movement「无自觉」的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:27.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是能力者在不知不觉中发散到周围的微小的力量的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的五感是无法感觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须使用专用的器械方可检测到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在在这个领域的研究已经在不断地在发展
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时能一起去「seventh mist」买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  风纪委员的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微晚一点没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巡逻的时候去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回不能这样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是这样的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你们每个人体内发散出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再稍微借些钱来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:22.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  前些天借给你的钱好像还没…还吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过会全部还你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我有钱了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:38.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无期限  无利息  无限制不是你的卖点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛就这么一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  在风纪委员来之前快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:49.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻松松啊  他们不是都在事后才来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  到底在干些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么风纪委员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你们无能我才会遭受这种待遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再多有点线索就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:23.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在知道的就只有「对方是大能力以上的能力者」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:23.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是书库找不到符合条件的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:29.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:33.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  是在短时间内突然大幅提升力量的能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  无论如何在短时间内是不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事根本不可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头开始对遗留物品检测一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟黑子一样  初春同学也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然今天也请她一起来买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  在抓到爆炸狂人之前也是没办法的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:31.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点  不知所以然的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:38.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春和白井同学作为风纪委员一直在努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:38.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而御坂学姐是很厉害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得「我完全没什么用啊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:51.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  抱歉  其实也没那么沉重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:54.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…如果我也有能力的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常生活会不会有所改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有「幻想御手」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为超能力也就不是梦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前谈论过的都市传说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是可以把能力的等级轻而易举地提高的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然连脱衣女都存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想说不定真的存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能存在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:27.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟姐姐大人一起买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:40.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个那天都不用当班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就跟佐天同学说「就当让她们放松一下怎么样」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:44.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:50.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  虽然很难得还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再稍微调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:56.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:00.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崭新的世界即将来临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将会拯救我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来白井同学没有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有拯救我的风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学有什么想去看看的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:10.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…也没什么特别想去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵！像这样的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的东西怎么能穿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:31.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了这个即便让我掀了裙子也能堂堂正正地让周围的人看了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别让人看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别掀起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:40.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  御坂学姐  有什么想看的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:42.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:44.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看一下睡衣之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  是这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然逛过很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是没找到一件好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来看看  这个好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春过来看一下这件睡衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:14.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样小孩子气的款式现在已经没有人穿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在小学生的时候还是穿着这种款式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:19.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的确有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:24.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的也是呢  都已经是中学生了怎么可能穿这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳衣在那边就有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:34.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:37.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是睡衣  又不是让人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:43.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学这个有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:50.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊噼里啪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:59.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为为为什么你会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:01.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能来么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:03.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是常盘台的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  丢了包的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？  你有妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听这孩子说想找洋装店就给她带路来到这里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  是哥哥带我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:31.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能像电视里面的人一样穿着洋装的打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:36.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  像现在这副打扮也很漂亮可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:39.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟某位穿短裤的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  想打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:43.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么之前悬而未决的决斗就在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:48.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你的脑子里就只有这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算在这人员密集的地方开打么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥  我想去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  大姐姐  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  出什么事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:20.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:33.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到那家伙就总是控制不住情绪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:36.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  完全就不像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:13:00.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是使用了相同作案手法的不同犯人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说说罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是各起事件间都难以找到联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:10.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不抓紧的话  又会有新的受害者出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得掌握些线索才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同事中可是有九人负了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:20.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说你不觉得太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道犯人的目标是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视卫星观测到有重力子的活动加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  你的手机有没有响？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:39.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:41.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  虚空爆炸事件有新情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:50.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园都市的监视卫星观测到重力子出现剧烈的加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观…观测地点在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在请求附近的警备员紧急出动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  请把观测地点告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是第七学区的洋装店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「seventh mist」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「seventh mist」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  我现在就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去把客人们疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:13.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静地听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:28.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经知道犯人的下一个袭击目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:31.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你协助我进行人群的避难工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:36.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学就赶紧去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春你也要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的目标是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位顾客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于店内的电路系统发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:03.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事出突然  今日的营业时间到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:06.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人员会为客人指示出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么故障啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家才刚刚到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:12.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噼里啪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说还留在店里么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:22.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:32.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有顾客都成功撤离了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在马上离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在过去的事件中的人员损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有风纪委员而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人真正的目标是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身处观测地点附近的风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的目标就是你啊  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:01.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:06.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个戴着眼镜的大哥哥让我交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃  那是炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超电磁炮把炸弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:17.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:31.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是最近的那个连续炸弹袭击事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面好像还有人没有撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员可真靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:35.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(270,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险  请退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐能够掌握更强大的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再增加点数量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是无能的风纪委员还是那群不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:59.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个不剩地全部炸飞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:13.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你有什么事就不需要我再多嘴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:18.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹狂人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:23.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我完全就听不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:26.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  就威力来说还真是不可小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说伤亡者了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连个受到擦伤的人都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我的最大输出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从外面一眼就能看出炸弹的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:48.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才会以为里面的人难以幸免啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超…超电磁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(342,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:06.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到常盘台的王牌登场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:08.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当我想做些什么的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:14.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会被力量彻底打趴在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你这样的人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:20.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:24.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有力量的家伙有哪一个不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你满口力量  力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把牙关咬紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:42.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打了也是活该
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:58.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她最不屑的  就是像你这种将力量当做挡箭牌的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:00.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘台的超电磁炮当初也不过是个低能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:05.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,328)\fs18}Level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:07.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她通过不同寻常的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终造就了一身被称作超能力者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:15.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  哪怕她只是一个低能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:15.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(416,328)\fs18}Level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:19.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人也会挡在你的面前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:45.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:46.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:50.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  多亏了御坂学姐  你看我毫发无伤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是常盘台的大姐姐救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:55.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:57.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:58.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:03.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  竟然只有初春她们所在的地方得以幸免
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要如何使用能力才能做到这个地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:21.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可真是立了大功一件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:31.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姐姐大人无论说什么黑子都会照做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮您刷背也好  按摩也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么您尽管提
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你的欲望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:40.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时  我的超电磁炮没能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:22.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:37.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正救下初春她们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:42.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:47.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中埋伏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:49.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:50.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:55.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都以为是我保护了那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名字的话就是「英雄」了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:01.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:05.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大家都没事  还在意那些干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:08.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁救的不都一样么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.25,0:23:24.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是在耍帅罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:26.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还偏偏只对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:29.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:32.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  那家伙总是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:33.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:36.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是面红耳赤的时候  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:36.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁面红耳赤了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:38.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:39.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是指夕阳


